OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772718050
OL,3,CFirst robotic hysterectomies carried
OL,4,Cout at hospital in Margate
OL,6,FSurgeons at the Queen Elizabeth The
OL,7,FQueen Mother Hospital in Margate have
OL,8,Fcarried out their first robot-assisted
OL,9,Fhysterectomies.
OL,11,FGynae-oncology consultants Fani Kokka
OL,12,Fand Rema Iyer operated using the
OL,13,FMedtronic Hugo robot, which was
OL,14,Finstalled this year.
OL,16,FConsultant Rema Iyer said the benefits
OL,17,Finclude more precision and control, as
OL,18,Fwell as faster recovery and a lower
OL,19,Frisk of infection.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
