FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772718050
OL,3,CFirst robotic hysterectomies carried
OL,4,Cout at hospital in Margate
OL,6,FShe said: "I am delighted to be able
OL,7,Fto offer robotic-assisted surgery to
OL,8,Four patients.
OL,10,F"The benefits are wide-ranging, from
OL,11,Ffaster recovery and lower risk of
OL,12,Finfection, to more precision and
OL,13,Fcontrol.
OL,15,F"This means there is less tissue
OL,16,Ftrauma and greater accuracy. This
OL,17,Finvestment in the latest technology
OL,18,Fmeans we are able to provide safer,
OL,19,Fmore advanced care to our communities
OL,20,Fand will also help us recruit more
OL,21,Fconsultants to join us in east Kent."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
