OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772718050
OL,3,CFirst robotic hysterectomies carried
OL,4,Cout at hospital in Margate
OL,6,FKirstine Goldsack from Canterbury was
OL,7,Fone of the first patients to have the
OL,8,Fprocedure and was able to go home the
OL,9,Fnext day.
OL,11,FThe 56-year-old opted to have her womb
OL,12,Fremoved after experiencing bleeding
OL,13,Ffollowing the menopause.
OL,15,FShe said: "I was a little bit
OL,16,Fapprehensive at first when Miss Iyer
OL,17,Fsaid it would be with the robot, but I
OL,18,Fwas also curious.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772718050
OL,3,CFirst robotic hysterectomies carried
OL,4,Cout at hospital in Margate
OL,6,F"Technology is always moving on and it
OL,7,Ffelt good to be able to play a part in
OL,8,Fhelping with the advancements.
OL,10,F"Recovery is going well, and each day
OL,11,Fis a step further, and I can get out
OL,12,Fand about and eat whatever I want.
OL,14,F"It's been a really positive
OL,15,Fexperience and I'm very grateful to
OL,16,FMiss Iyer and the team for giving me
OL,17,Fthe opportunity to be one of the first
OL,18,Fpatients."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772718050
OL,3,CFirst robotic hysterectomies carried
OL,4,Cout at hospital in Margate
OL,6,FKirstine, had tried other treatments
OL,7,Fto control the bleeding but nothing
OL,8,Fhad worked.
OL,10,FShe continued: "I gave everything that
OL,11,Fwas suggested a good go, but nothing
OL,12,Fseemed to conquer it.
OL,14,F"It was affecting my quality of life;
OL,15,FI wanted to enjoy my grandchild and to
OL,16,Fplan things but I could never predict
OL,17,Fhow I would feel.
OL,19,F"It got to the point where I had
OL,20,Fenough, and a hysterectomy felt like
OL,21,Fthe best way to resolve it."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
